<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>領収書</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 15mm;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 15px 0;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #333;
    }
    
    .receipt-info {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .receipt-info .row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .receipt-info .left,
    .receipt-info .right {
      width: 48%;
    }
    
    .recipient {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .amount-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px 0;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 3px solid #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    
    .amount-section p {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .amount {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2e7d32;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    
    .amount-description {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    
    .company-info {
      margin-top: 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    
    .company-info .left,
    .company-info .right {
      width: 48%;
    }
    
    .company-info h4 {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .details-section {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .details-section h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    }
    
    .details-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 10px;
    }
    
    .details-table th,
    .details-table td {
      padding: 6px;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    
    .details-table th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .details-table .number {
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>領収書</h1>
    <p>Receipt</p>
  </div>

  <div class="receipt-info">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left">
        <div class="recipient">
          <%= invoice.invoice_recipient.name %> 様
        </div>
        <% if invoice.invoice_recipient.department.present? %>
          <p><%= invoice.invoice_recipient.department %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="right" style="text-align: right;">
        <p><strong>領収書番号:</strong> REC-<%= invoice.id.to_s.rjust(6, '0') %></p>
        <p><strong>発行日:</strong> <%= Date.current.strftime("%Y年%m月%d日") %></p>
        <p><strong>対象月:</strong> <%= invoice.target_month_display %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="amount-section">
    <p>下記の通り領収いたしました</p>
    <div class="amount">¥<%= number_with_delimiter(invoice.total_amount) %>-</div>
    <div class="amount-description">（<%= invoice.target_month_display %>分インセンティブ）</div>
  </div>

  <% if bonus_details.any? %>
  <div class="details-section">
    <h3>インセンティブ明細</h3>
    <table class="details-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>購入ID</th>
          <th>日付</th>
          <th>種別</th>
          <th>販売者</th>
          <th>商品名</th>
          <th class="number">数量</th>
          <th class="number">単価</th>
          <th class="number">金額</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% bonus_details.each do |detail| %>
        <tr>
          <td>#<%= detail[:purchase_id] %></td>
          <td><%= detail[:purchased_at].strftime("%m/%d") %></td>
          <td><%= detail[:type] %></td>
          <td><%= detail[:user_name] %></td>
          <td><%= detail[:product_name] %></td>
          <td class="number"><%= detail[:quantity] %></td>
          <td class="number">¥<%= number_with_delimiter(detail[:unit_bonus].round) %></td>
          <td class="number">¥<%= number_with_delimiter(detail[:total_bonus]) %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
      </tbody>
      <tfoot>
        <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0; font-weight: bold;">
          <td colspan="7">合計</td>
          <td class="number">¥<%= number_with_delimiter(bonus_details.sum { |d| d[:total_bonus] }) %></td>
        </tr>
      </tfoot>
    </table>
  </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="company-info">
    <div class="left">
      <h4>発行者</h4>
      <p><strong>株式会社アジアビジネストラスト</strong></p>
      <p>〒104-0061</p>
      <p>東京都中央区銀座4丁目8－1銀座鶴月ビル3階</p>
      <p>TEL: 03-5904-8148</p>
      <p>Email: abt1@asia-b-t.com</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="right">
      <h4>但し書き</h4>
      <p>インセンティブ報酬として</p>
      
      <h4 style="margin-top: 30px;">備考</h4>
      <p>※ 本領収書は再発行いたしません。</p>
      <p>※ 大切に保管してください。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>この領収書は電子的に発行されたものです。</p>
    <p>ご不明な点がございましたら、上記連絡先までお問い合わせください。</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>